---
This application speaks to DCS-BIOS (https://github.com/dcs-bios/dcs-bios, GPL v2)
and is part of the OpenSkyhawk project (https://github.com/OpenSkyHawk), whose
firmware is likewise GPL v2-or-later. It bundles generated control-reference data
derived from the OpenSkyhawk firmware. DCS-Skunkworks/Bort (GPL-3.0) is referenced
as a design precedent only — no Bort source is copied.
